jellyfin-external-player (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Remove VLC support, simplify to mpv-only
  * Auto-detect mpv location on Windows (Scoop, Chocolatey, Program Files)
  * Auto-focus mpv window on Windows after playback starts
  * Fix Windows console window flash and logging issues
  * Add DEB_SIGN option for flexible package signing

